com.jaunt.component
Class FormComponent

java.lang.Object
  com.jaunt.component.FormComponent
Direct Known Subclasses:
ButtonComponent, FieldComponent, FileComponent, ImageComponent, SelectComponent, TextAreaComponent
public abstract class FormComponent
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract class representing a form's component (eg, textfield, radiobutton, or any other component which, as an HTML/XHTML Element, supports the name attribute).

Since:
0.9.0
Author:
Tom Cervenka
